1
00:00:51,720 --> 00:00:52,520
How is the situation?

2
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,000
Right now

3
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:56,240
Khun Khaeng Khae has taken Lookkai away.

4
00:00:57,360 --> 00:00:58,160
I don't know where they've gone by now.

5
00:00:59,680 --> 00:01:02,360
Khun Khaeng Khae really is the root cause of everything.

6
00:01:02,800 --> 00:01:03,240
Yes.

7
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:05,760
And this time, I'm certain

8
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:08,600
that she's going to do something truly terrible.

9
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:13,880
Anyway

10
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:15,920
Mr. Lawyer, could I ask you

11
00:01:15,920 --> 00:01:17,200
to look after Madame?

12
00:01:18,640 --> 00:01:19,840
I need to go after those two first.

13
00:01:20,960 --> 00:01:21,760
Understood.

14
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,840
Well, well, well.

15
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:34,440
Didn't you say you wouldn't do this kind of work anymore?

16
00:01:36,800 --> 00:01:37,720
No, Auntie.

17
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:39,000
I said

18
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:41,280
if I want to do it,

19
00:01:41,800 --> 00:01:42,720
I will.

20
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,600
But if I don't want to

21
00:01:44,720 --> 00:01:45,640
I won't.

22
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,800
But I know

23
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,320
there's one thing

24
00:01:51,320 --> 00:01:54,200
that you really want to do.

25
00:01:57,440 --> 00:01:58,960
What do you mean, Auntie?

26
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:03,160
The very special meal

27
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:05,680
for Khun Pakin, of course.

28
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:07,400
If that's what you mean

29
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:09,680
I probably don't want to do it anymore.

30
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,200
Well, suit yourself.

31
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:14,240
I'm just telling you to do you a favor.

32
00:02:15,160 --> 00:02:18,080
Because I was afraid someone might cook and wait for nothing.

33
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,840
Because today

34
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:24,640
he won't be coming back for dinner.

35
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,520
Where did he go?

36
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,920
See? Curious, aren't we?

37
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:30,680
He said

38
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,760
he went to make merit

39
00:02:32,760 --> 00:02:34,280
for Pakinai's 50th day

40
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,120
or something like that.

41
00:02:35,440 --> 00:02:36,560
So he won't be back for dinner.

42
00:03:09,200 --> 00:03:10,000
This can't be real.

43
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,600
Damn it.

44
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,160
How could I be so stupid?

45
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,320
Hmm.

46
00:03:26,880 --> 00:03:27,680
(Sighs)

47
00:03:28,160 --> 00:03:30,000
What's the matter with you now, huh?

48
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:31,080
What's wrong?

49
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:32,520
What are you overthinking now?

50
00:03:32,760 --> 00:03:33,560
Huh?

51
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,480
Why even think about it?

52
00:03:35,480 --> 00:03:37,920
If it were me, I wouldn't give it a second thought.

53
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:40,520
Why give yourself a headache over it? Ugh.

54
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:42,960
Right now, you only have one job

55
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:45,680
take this opportunity and escape.

56
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,920
Go on, run away.

57
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:48,720
Well

58
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:50,840
part of me just wants to run away and be done with it.

59
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,760
But another part of me wants to stay and prove

60
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,320
Prove what?

61
00:03:56,280 --> 00:03:57,040
To prove that

62
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:59,080
everything I've said is the truth.

63
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:02,040
Someday, Khun Phakin has to know the truth.

64
00:04:04,360 --> 00:04:05,600
What's going on with you?/P’Dao

65
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,560
Lookkai!

66
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,680
Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait.

67
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,480
Who is this? Who are you?

68
00:04:11,480 --> 00:04:12,920
Where did you come from

69
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:13,520
and how did you get here?

70
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:15,800
This is not a public place. Get out!

71
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:18,160
Get out!

72
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:19,800
Khun Pakin sent me here.

73
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,800
What is going on, Lookkai?

74
00:04:21,800 --> 00:04:22,680
I'm so confused right now.

75
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,360
The truth is, Khun Pakin
finally knows the truth.

76
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,280
That P'Venus and P'Saturn

77
00:04:27,280 --> 00:04:28,280
are two different people.

78
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:39,040
Wait... so the story you've been telling me

79
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,040
was actually true?

80
00:04:42,520 --> 00:04:43,200
Really?

81
00:04:44,120 --> 00:04:45,440
Aunt Tammy.

82
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:48,280
I told you I don't know how many times

83
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,600
but you and Khun Pakin never believed me.

84
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:52,200
Do you believe me now?

85
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,480
Oh my god... Tammy..

86
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,640
Tammy is so confused right now.

87
00:04:57,640 --> 00:04:58,680
What the hell is going on?

88
00:04:59,440 --> 00:05:00,040
Wait, wait, wait.

89
00:05:00,400 --> 00:05:01,320
And right now

90
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,600
Where is Pakin?

91
00:05:04,200 --> 00:05:06,040
Where is he?

92
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,920
Khun Pakin said

93
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:09,800
he feels incredibly guilty
towards you, P'Dao.

94
00:05:10,080 --> 00:05:11,400
He wants to apologize to you.

95
00:05:12,200 --> 00:05:13,880
But he asked not to do it here.

96
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:15,560
Because this place

97
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,240
is filled with terrible memories.

98
00:05:21,840 --> 00:05:22,200
And...

99
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:23,680
did Khun Pakin say anything else?

100
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:25,960
Khun Pakin said

101
00:05:26,400 --> 00:05:27,200
he will wait

102
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,160
until the deadline he has set.

103
00:05:29,720 --> 00:05:31,120
if you don't show up by then

104
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:33,760
he will never see you ever again.

105
00:05:38,920 --> 00:05:39,720
Lookkai.

106
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,120
Take me to Khun Pakin right now.

107
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:45,800
Got it.

108
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:49,680
Whoa...

109
00:05:52,760 --> 00:05:54,120
I'm not dreaming.

110
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:56,200
It's real. It's the truth.

111
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:57,840
They really are two different people.

112
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,120
Oh my god

113
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,600
Tammy...

114
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:02,240
Yes, Khun Khaeng Khae.

115
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:04,480
Everything is going exactly as we expected.

116
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,520
What do you want me to do next, Khun Khaeng Khae?

117
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,640
Just give the word.

118
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,320
Understood.

119
00:06:13,400 --> 00:06:15,120
I will make my move right away.

120
00:06:26,240 --> 00:06:27,040
Venus

121
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:31,640
Venus

122
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:34,840
Venus

123
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:42,080
Venus

124
00:06:44,840 --> 00:06:46,200
Venus

125
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,040
Venus

126
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,120
Venus

127
00:06:54,680 --> 00:06:55,480
Where are you?!

128
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,400
Pakin.

129
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:58,840
What's wrong?

130
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,840
Why are you making such a racket, huh?

131
00:07:02,080 --> 00:07:03,200
What's the matter with you?

132
00:07:03,200 --> 00:07:04,280
Aunt Tammy, wait! / Huh?

133
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,160
Tell me first

134
00:07:06,160 --> 00:07:07,160
where is Venus?

135
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,600
Hey.

136
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:10,480
Hmm.

137
00:07:11,760 --> 00:07:12,480
Are you delirious?

138
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:14,000
Are you crazy, insane

139
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,120
or just sleep-deprived, huh?

140
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:18,320
You were the one who had people come pick him up!

141
00:07:18,520 --> 00:07:20,000
Why are you looking for him now?

142
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:23,400
Listen, Aunt Tammy.

143
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:24,040
Yeah?

144
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:25,000
If Venuscomes back

145
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:26,440
do not let him go anywhere

146
00:07:26,440 --> 00:07:27,480
with anyone else ever again!

147
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:28,960
Got it?

148
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,600
What the hell is his problem?
